{"tid":1364093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【RPG】如果你係牛屎佬, 你最驚會係咩? 警察? 示威者? 係窮呀DLGH!!","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:47:28.000Z","uid":264624,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca15903c7f4a441c160ad71d28b50ee0166b5202","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:37:29.000Z","msg":"只要攪到元朗經濟蕭條<br />\n日撚日好似722咁變死城<br />\n樓價暴跌有樓冇人租冇人買<br />\n隨時班牛屎佬自己走出嚟玩割蓆<br />\n<br />\n打打殺殺坐監係佢哋日常<br />\n我哋幾萬人衝入去佢哋唔撚會驚<br />\n當日打唔嬴咪之後覆桌<br />\n佢哋殺人放火都唔會有事 驚條撚<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋係會為咗幾千蚊就做咁大單嘢<br />\n總言之全部都係錢錢錢<br />\n冇利益既嘢佢哋唔會做<br />\n有著數既祠堂都賣得<br />\n<br />\n個個都識得屌飯民遊行咗十幾廿年無撚用<br />\n而家勇武咪一撚樣<br />\n衝咗咁多次  爭取到啲咩<br />\n係咪又要學飯民咁衝多十年八件先覺醒<br />\n<br />\n和理非  要<br />\n勇武  要<br />\n但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>智謀先係最重要</strong></span></span><br />\n策略正確  無論係攻係守都會有成效<br />\n用錯方法  就算冇埋條命都唔會爭取到任何嘢"},{"pid":"8468a75e34c094e4adb3688385e31e0059e1ce7d","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04876debe9e9f35b91c52d79402dfae833939045","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd3f9a3161dfc6e70045624e14a84a88c996397","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89989cce16032ca71ef56b39201ded8d71f81fa9","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30154916a832ab19b4b6223f4b7ea3f3917403b6","tid":1364093,"uid":264624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":